data.description: This 4 bedrooms, 2 bathroom home sits on a beautiful 2.8 acre lot in a country subdivision just outside of North Judson. It has a large pond that adds a beautiful outdoor element for all your entertaining needs. The home has large vaulted ceilings and a fireplace that creates a beautiful and spacious living area and adds warmth and coziness for those cold days. Leading into the spacious, open concept kitchen with a breakfast bar and dining area. An oversize master bedroom features a walk-in closet and a private bathroom, offering a luxurious retreat. With the laundry room conveniently located on the main floor, everyday chores are a breeze. Upstairs, you'll find another bedroom, providing ample space for various uses, from a bedroom to a home office or recreation room.This home is equipped with a geothermal HVAC system, offering maximum efficiency. 2-car garage provides secure parking and storage space. A screened back porch offers a peaceful vantage point to gaze upon the serene country fields and creating a perfect spot for relaxation and taking in the picturesque surroundings. Schedule a viewing today and experience the exceptional features and modern convenience this home has to offer.
